<div class="body">
<pre>
とみたです。

On Mon, 24 May 2004 04:29:47 +0900
Hideki Hayashi &lt;loneliness@xxxxxxxxxx&gt; wrote:

<span class="quote1">&gt; 例えば、以下の様なデータで、直前のデーターと直後のデータを取得したいの</span>
<span class="quote1">&gt; ですが。</span>
<span class="quote1">&gt; 何か良いsql文はないでしょうか？</span>
<span class="quote1">&gt; </span>
<span class="quote1">&gt; ------------------------</span>
<span class="quote1">&gt; id	data</span>
<span class="quote1">&gt; ------------------------</span>
<span class="quote1">&gt; 1	aaaaa</span>
<span class="quote1">&gt; 3	bbbbb	</span>
<span class="quote1">&gt; 4	ccccc  現在の位置(SELECT * FROM table WHERE id = 4)</span>
<span class="quote1">&gt; 9	ddddd</span>
<span class="quote1">&gt; ------------------------</span>

何のひねりもないですが (^^; こんな感じでどうでしょうか。

mysql&gt; select * from t where id &lt; 4 order by id desc limit 1;
+------+------+
<span class="quote1">| id   | data |</span>
+------+------+
<span class="quote1">|    3 | bbbb |</span>
+------+------+

mysql&gt; select * from t where id &gt; 4 order by id limit 1;
+------+------+
<span class="quote1">| id   | data |</span>
+------+------+
<span class="quote1">|    9 | dddd |</span>
+------+------+

